      "review_summary": "The PR adds trailing `notify=false` parsing in Telegram `deliverReplies`, strips the marker from reply text, forwards marker-derived silent delivery to plain text sends, and adds focused delivery tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +23, Tests +31. Total +54 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level. Current heartbeat sends use `sendDurableMessageBatch` into the Telegram outbound adapter, while this PR changes `deliverReplies`; the media branch also visibly keeps `params.silent` instead of marker-derived silent intent.",
